item.author: 作者
item.description: 由于之前有写过一键安装jupyter的shell脚本，所以这里只需要找一个服务器就够了 https://github.com/spiritLHLS/one-click-installation-script#%E4%B8%80%E9%94%AE%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85jupyter%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83 1 curl -L https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiritLHLS/one-click-installation-script/main/install_scripts/jupyter.sh -o jupyter.sh && chmod +x jupyter.sh && bash jupyter.sh 又由于之前玩Linux积攒
